{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e120c0a8b1","title":"国家计委关于引进彩色电视和转播设备的报告","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"53dffc5628","index":0,"year":1973,"month":5,"day":19,"articleId":"e120c0a8b1"}],"tags":[{"id":"33f01f9c5a","name":"李先念","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"00ac7f4666","name":"〔73〕计生字166"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"93ac49436a","type":"title","text":"国家计委关于引进彩色电视和转播设备的报告","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"f2967e9dd6","type":"authors","text":"〔73〕计生字166","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"2c5211064d","type":"paragraph","text":"去年7月和10月，经先念同志批准，从国外引进彩色电视和转播设备36项，共计533万美元。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"bb0ec7c925","type":"paragraph","text":"到目前止，大部分设备已经订妥，还有一部分设备正在谈判。由于当时估价偏低和美元贬值等原因，原批外汇已不够用，广播局对所提设备进行压缩后，仍缺92万美元。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"9b56dfcba3","type":"paragraph","text":" （此件系向李先念、纪登奎、华国锋并国务院的报告）","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"0d058d9b20","type":"appellation","text":"附  件","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"36a4eefc16","type":"subtitle","text":"李先念同志1973年5月21日批示","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"},{"id":"b067ddf66d","type":"paragraph","text":"拟同意，登奎、国锋同志批。要下决心搞上去。进口一些设备，也是为了有利于自力更生。把自力更生的观念减弱了，那是非常错误的。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1"}],"page":{"id":"333eceae4e","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"e120c0a8b1","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}